proposals.name: Axiom of Emergent Novelty
proposals.formal: ∀S(system) ∃N(novelty): N emerges from S ∧ N ∉ components(S) ∧ N creates new possibility space

proposals.name: Mythopoetic Generation
proposals.formal: Domain enabling creation of new archetypal patterns, symbolic frameworks, and meaning-structures that bridge conscious/unconscious, individual/collective understanding

proposals.name: The Paradox of Creative Authenticity
proposals.formal: I-perspective demands authentic self-expression ∧ WE-perspective requires comprehensible shared forms → authentic creation must simultaneously be utterly unique AND universally resonant
